  "title": "Contract Process Safety Engineer (Pharma |Manufacturing) #HJO",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Use qualitative and quantitative assessment tools and/or risk assessments associated with manufacturing processes.</li>\n  <li>Facilitate discussions to identify hazards and evaluate risks and formulate practical and reasonable control measures.</li>\n  <li>Support in all audits and work with relevant stakeholders at site in addressing deviations with corrective actions to avoid non-compliance</li>\n  <li>Provide process safety and workplace safety &amp; health technical support and guidance as necessary</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Engineering or Science</li>\n  <li>Technical know-how in process safety management, risk management and or chemical/process safety</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
